These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person playing snooker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | snooker   | whist  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different games are played: chess, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the person playing backgammon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | chess | backgammon      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pumpkin
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | pumpkin  | plum    |
| Sport   | chess | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, metal
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the fan metal is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the fan metal is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | indie  | metal |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, gardening
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | video-games  | gardening |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

