The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, action
1. the fan d&b is on the far right##1
2. the fan indie is not the person watching documentary movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | d&b      |
| Nationality   | action | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill
2 different pets are kept: goat, hamster
1. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the bongani-smoker is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | bongani | dunhill |
| Pet   | goat       | hamster       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-8::.
