There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
2. the japanese is not the person who's birthday is in august##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Food          | december     | august  |
| Nationality   | japanese | mexican |

